'''费利佩·费雷拉·利马'''（{{lang-pt|Felipe Ferreira Lima}}，{{bd|1985年|4月5日||}}）生于马托格罗索州库亚巴，是一名巴西男子游泳运动员，主攻蛙泳<ref name="OlympicBotGeneratedRef">{{cite web|title=Felipe Lima|url=http://www.london2012.com/athlete/lima-felipe-1073087/|work=London 2012|accessdate=2012-09-13|deadurl=yes|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120913101142/http://www.london2012.com/athlete/lima-felipe-1073087/|archive-date=2012-09-13}}</ref>。他在童年时曾接触过[[体操|体操]]、[[足球|足球]]等运动<ref name="olimpianos">{{cite web|url=http://www.olimpianos.com.br/consulta_verb.php?&cod=560&mod=Nata%E7%E3o|title=FELIPE LIMA|work={{lang|pt|Atletas Olímpicos Brasileiros}}|accessdate=2020-07-07|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170214102729/http://www.olimpianos.com.br/consulta_verb.php?&cod=560&mod=Nata%E7%E3o|archivedate=2017-02-14|dead-url=no}}</ref>。12岁时，他被母亲带到一家游泳学校里开始练习游泳<ref name="fina">{{cite web|url=https://www.fina.org/athletes/felipe-lima|title=Felipe Lima|work=[[国际游泳联合会|FINA]]|accessdate=2020-07-07|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20191216080938/https://www.fina.org/athletes/felipe-lima|archivedate=2019-12-16|dead-url=no}}</ref>。15岁时，他参加自己运动生涯的首个全国锦标赛<ref name="olimpianos"/>。

2019年1月16日，利马宣布加入美国国籍，此前他在已在[[美国|美国]]居住多年。<ref name="fina"/><ref>{{cite web|url=https://swimswam.com/brazilian-olympian-felipe-lima-becomes-us-citizen/|title=Brazilian Olympian Felipe Lima Becomes U.S. Citizen|work=SwimSwam|date=2019-01-17|accessdate=2020-07-07|archiveurl=https://archive.today/20200707094333/https://swimswam.com/brazilian-olympian-felipe-lima-becomes-us-citizen/|archivedate=2020-07-07|dead-url=no}}</ref>

